on-arrival: next_election_time = time+3; next_election_month = month + 3; next_election_year = year; next_election_year = year + 1 if next_election_month > 12; next_election_month = next_election_month - 12 if next_election_month > 12; new_middle_labour -= 5; old_middle_labour -= 5; workers_labour -= 3; catholics_labour -= 3; in_election = 1

Since the remaining bourgeois and right-wing parties cannot form a tolerable governing agreement, new elections have been called for [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +]. The previous chancellor has resigned, and has been replaced by Heinrich Brüning, also of the Center Party, ruling as part of a presidential cabinet. 

We are seen as responsible for the failure to form a government, and many of our middle-class and even some working-class supporters have deserted the party.


@ministries

We can pick from any number of ministries. Controlling a ministry allows us to directly effect policy in that area. [? if in_left_front : Any ministry that we do not take will be given to the CPGB. ?] [? if in_left_front and reichswehr_minister_party == "CPGB" : If the CPGB controls the Reichswehr Ministry, the army will most likely revolt. ?]

